<div class="container">
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>Welcome to <strong>Japan Travel Insights</strong>. Our mission is to provide authentic, deep-dive travel information for English-speaking visitors to Japan.</p>

    <p>We focus on helping you discover not just the famous landmarks, but the hidden stories and local secrets that make Japan truly special. Whether it's your first trip or your tenth, we aim to be your trusted companion in exploring the Land of the Rising Sun.</p>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Authenticity:</strong> We provide insights from a local perspective.</li>
      <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We promote responsible tourism and crowd-avoidance strategies.</li>
      <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Our guides are carefully crafted to be practical and easy to follow.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Join us as we explore the beauty, tradition, and modern marvels of Japan, one story at a time.</p>
  </div>
